    <div class="module_container module_container--outer">
        
       
        <div class="module_container module_container--inner">
            <h2 class="module-details_title">
                <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblModuleDetailHeadline">Altria Reports 2020 Third-Quarter And Nine-Months Results; Tobacco Businesses Demonstrate Resilience; Narrows 2020 Full-Year Earnings Guidance</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="module_container module_container--content">
                <div class="module_date-time">
                    <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblDate" class="module_date-text">10/30/2020</span>
                </div>
                <div class="module_links module_q4-icon-links">
                    <div class="module_related-document">
                        <a href="//s204.q4cdn.com/505541855/files/doc_news/2020/10/20Q3-release.pdf" id="_ctrl0_ctl39_hrefDownload" class="module_link module_news-details_download" target="_blank">
                            <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblDownload" class="module_link-text">Download this Press Release</span>
                            <span class="sr-only">PDF Format (opens in new window)</span>
                            <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblDocument" class="module_file-size">PDF 386 KB</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div id="_ctrl0_ctl39_ulAttachments" class="module_attachments">
                        
                                
                                <a href="https://services.choruscall.com/links/mo201030.html" id="_ctrl0_ctl39_rptAttachments_ctl00_hrefOnline" target="_blank" class="module_link">Webcast</a>
                            
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="module_body">
                    <style type="text/css">.q4default .bwalignc { text-align: center; list-style-position: inside }.q4default .bwalignl { text-align: left }.q4default .bwalignr { text-align: right; list-style-position: inside }.q4default .bwblockalignl { margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto }.q4default .bwcellpmargin { margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px }.q4default .bwdoublebottom { border-bottom: double black 2.25pt }.q4default .bwleftsingle { border-left: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwlistcircle { list-style-type: circle }.q4default .bwlistdisc { list-style-type: disc }.q4default .bwpadl0 { padding-left: 0px }.q4default .bwpadl1 { padding-left: 5px }.q4default .bwpadl2 { padding-left: 10px }.q4default .bwpadl3 { padding-left: 15px }.q4default .bwpadl4 { padding-left: 20px }.q4default .bwpadr0 { padding-right: 0px }.q4default .bwrightsingle { border-right: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwrowaltcolor0 { background-color: #cceeff }.q4default .bwsinglebottom { border-bottom: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwtablemarginb { margin-bottom: 10px }.q4default .bwtopsingle { border-top: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwuline { text-decoration: underline }.q4default .bwvertalignb { vertical-align: bottom }.q4default .bwwidth1 { width: 1% }.q4default .bwwidth10 { width: 10% }.q4default .bwwidth100 { width: 100% }.q4default .bwwidth11 { width: 11% }.q4default .bwwidth12 { width: 12% }.q4default .bwwidth13 { width: 13% }.q4default .bwwidth18 { width: 18% }.q4default .bwwidth19 { width: 19% }.q4default .bwwidth2 { width: 2% }.q4default .bwwidth22 { width: 22% }.q4default .bwwidth23 { width: 23% }.q4default .bwwidth24 { width: 24% }.q4default .bwwidth26 { width: 26% }.q4default .bwwidth3 { width: 3% }.q4default .bwwidth31 { width: 31% }.q4default .bwwidth35 { width: 35% }.q4default .bwwidth37 { width: 37% }.q4default .bwwidth4 { width: 4% }.q4default .bwwidth42 { width: 42% }.q4default .bwwidth5 { width: 5% }.q4default .bwwidth51 { width: 51% }.q4default .bwwidth53 { width: 53% }.q4default .bwwidth54 { width: 54% }.q4default .bwwidth55 { width: 55% }.q4default .bwwidth57 { width: 57% }.q4default .bwwidth58 { width: 58% }.q4default .bwwidth6 { width: 6% }.q4default .bwwidth61 { width: 61% }.q4default .bwwidth62 { width: 62% }.q4default .bwwidth64 { width: 64% }.q4default .bwwidth65 { width: 65% }.q4default .bwwidth7 { width: 7% }.q4default .bwwidth73 { width: 73% }.q4default .bwwidth75 { width: 75% }.q4default .bwwidth77 { width: 77% }.q4default .bwwidth78 { width: 78% }.q4default .bwwidth8 { width: 8% }.q4default .bwwidth9 { width: 9% }</style><div class="q4default"><p>    RICHMOND, Va.--(BUSINESS WIRE)--
Altria Group, Inc. (Altria) (NYSE: MO) today announces its 2020 third-quarter and nine-months business results and narrows its 2020 adjusted diluted earnings per share (EPS) guidance.
</p><p>
“Altria continued to demonstrate its resilience during the third quarter while navigating the challenges presented by the COVID-19 pandemic,” said Billy Gifford, Altria’s Chief Executive Officer. “In the third quarter, our tobacco businesses delivered strong financial performance once again and we continued to make progress against our 10-year Vision.”
</p><p>
“Based on our year-to-date results and insight into an additional quarter of ABI earnings contributions, we’re narrowing our full-year 2020 adjusted diluted EPS guidance by raising the lower end of the range. We now expect to deliver adjusted diluted EPS in a range of $4.30 to $4.38, representing a growth rate of 2% to 4% from an adjusted diluted EPS base of $4.21 in 2019.”
</p><p>
