  <li>
Oral tobacco products segment retail share was 49.9% and <i>Copenhagen</i> continued to be the leading oral tobacco brand with a retail share of 31.8%. Share losses for both the segment and <i>Copenhagen</i> were due to the growth of oral nicotine pouches.
</li>
